# Running AlphaFold on Biocommons Galaxy

## Austrlalian Biocommons

The [Australian Biocommons](https://www.biocommons.org.au/) is a digital capability aimed at enhancing Australian research in its ability to understand the molecular basis of life across environmental, agricultural and biomedical science.

## Galaxy Australia
[Galaxy Australia](https://usegalaxy.org.au/login/start?redirect=None) is an open, web-based platform for accessible, reproducible and transparent computational research.

https://site.usegalaxy.org.au/request/alphafold

## AlphaFold on Galaxy
In https://usegalaxy.org.au/ Navigate to ALphaFold.
Fill in the form and click Run Tool!

Once you submit a session, you can then share the results:
https://usegalaxy.org.au/datasets/a6e389a98c2d1678f2d92efc723dec14/preview
